http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Public speaking, parliamentary procedure, organization, delegation, oral communication, conflict resolution, business etiquette, and community service are major topics to assist students in development of their leadership skills for the future. Opportunities are provided for students to participate in FFA and supervised experience activities.
